  "translations": {
    "en": "He said: Abul Hasan Ali ibn Bilal al-Mahlabi reported to me, he said: Ali ibn Abdillah ibn Asad al-Isfahani narrated to us, he said: Ibrahim ibn Muhammad al-Thaqafi narrated to us, he said: Ismail ibn Aban narrated to us, he said: al-Sabbah ibn Yahya al-Muzani narrated to us, from al-A'mash, from al-Minhal ibn Amr, from Abbad ibn Abdillah, who said:",
